            <bindingDesc>
              <binding>
                <p>Contemporary calf blind-stamped in the Florentine style (modo fiorentino), with an ornamental pattern based on Islamic ropework, over wooden boards, with remnants of 4 pairs of ties.</p>
              </binding>
